<subSubSection pageId="58" pageNumber="816" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="58.[1451,2661,270,1371]" pageId="58" pageNumber="816">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1453,1802,1180,1209]" pageId="58" pageNumber="816">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red Lust (as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Hill" authorityYear="1968" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Pipistrellus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="58" pageNumber="816" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="eisentrauti">Pipistrellus eisentrauti</taxonomicName>
). There is considerable confusion surrounding the taxonomy and distribution ofthis species, and a full assessment is thus impossible meantime.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
